<沿革內容><![CDATA[1.Promulgated by the Ministry of Health and Welfare Order Wei-Shou-Shi-Tzu No.1061107539, on December 28, 2017; The Regulations shall be effective on the day of the promulgation.]]></沿革內容>
<前言><![CDATA[]]></前言>
<法規內容>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 1</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These regulations are promulgated pursuant to the Paragraph 4 of Article 53-1 of the Pharmaceutical Affairs Act.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 2</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The quality management of business undertakings engaged in wholesaling, retailing, importing and exporting western pharmaceuticals (hereinafter referred to as the business undertakings), shall meet the regulations of quality management standards indicated in Table 1 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 3</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The organization and personnel of the business undertakings shall meet the regulations of organization and personnel standards indicated in Table 2 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 4</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The premises and equipment of the business undertakings shall meet the regulations of premises and equipment standards indicated in Table 3 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 5</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The documentation of the business undertakings shall meet the regulations of documentation standards indicated in Table 4 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 6</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The operation procedures of the business undertakings shall meet the regulations of operation procedures standards indicated in Table 5 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 7</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The customer complaints, returns, and recalls of the business undertakings shall meet the regulations of complaints, returns, and recalls standards indicated in Table 7 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 8</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The outsourced activities of the business undertakings shall meet the regulations of outsourced activities standards indicated in Table 7 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 9</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The self-inspections of the business undertakings shall meet the regulations of self-inspections standards indicated in Table 8 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 10</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The transportation of the business undertakings shall meet the regulations of transportation standards indicated in Table 9 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 11</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[The definition of terms used in this regulation indicated in Table 10 (attached).
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
  <條文>
    <條號>Article 12</條號>
    <條文內容><![CDATA[These regulations shall be effective as of the date of promulgation.
]]></條文內容>
  </條文>
</法規內容>
